Here's the setup here for documentation: http://thisdavej.com/build-an-amazing-markdown-editor-using-visual-studio-code-and-pandoc/

For the ccc parts, see http://benjam.info/panam/

pandoc --css=styling.css -V lang=en -V highlighting-css= --mathjax \
       --smart --to=html5 input.md -o output.html

